{"title":"没头谣　黄安民谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":10,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"没头谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄安民谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燎荧辑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没头谣又名木头谣。所谓没头，有信口编来没头没尾之意。抗日时期的鄂豫皖民谣，经常有痛骂国民党反共军的，例如：“反共游击队，吃了饭就睡，日本来了往后退，头也不敢回。”下面这首没头谣，也是讲的这样的一个反动县长，人民在实际体验中把问题看得多么深刻，讲得多么清楚，仇恨又多么大。人民是最好的证人，又是债主，现在我军已经回到了黄安，正是总清算一切新旧血债的时候。所以，这首民谣，看来还是新鲜的，而且还有新的意义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋荣平，在黄安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七里坪，做县官。（注一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手下一层一，（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天高三尺三。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀人又放火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮得地皮穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓该死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爷加官。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百十条性命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"值不上他吃一餐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起来，难得说……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十个湾子，（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陡然变成青一色："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把火点去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧得么罗都没得（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚么是“匪区”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟同中国；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚么是“匪区”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除非天晓得！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈报剿了“匪”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面光是鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绑得法场去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民命不如水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——反共反人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里讲原委！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）当时蒋荣平只占了七里坪一隅之地，黄安绝大部分都是解放区，这几句话，有讽刺之意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）他手下只是乡长，所以叫做手下一层一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）湾子，就是村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）么罗，甚么的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群生意人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路过七里坪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当头碰到打劫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想进衙门诉冤情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县官把话论："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小辈且听真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定是‘奸匪’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫你来探信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"败坏俺官家名誉了不成！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是你的到来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是你的证？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果还不座位出（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要你命归阴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚罢，滚罢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫待老子发牛性！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜小百姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干巴和硬蹲，（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前站的“黑杆子”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是个“铁”“证”！（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是说出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要命不要命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着头鼠窜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路苦相劝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“背了时散摊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇着‘七月半’”？（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）即拿出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）意约干巴巴的在那里硬蹲着，形容无奈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）打劫实际是县官组织的所以有这段说法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）背时即运气不好，散摊即散伙，七月半俗称鬼过年，意即撞了鬼了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县官出巡二程乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那方百姓便遭殃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手令下给乡队长："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“扬威就要做‘三光’。”（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行辕住在乡公所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整天盘问“为什么？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“上官是‘匪区’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"么样不点一把火？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带些队子去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包管千万妥。”（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长胡承义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在有狠气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡长吴国义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟有权力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两“义”带队走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路做“成绩”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓不知何事起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"箱子柜子翻倒底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"值钱的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞上腰包里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颈高头仰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀武扬威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个敢望？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了上店，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下火线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承平局面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然转变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡队长放哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓该倒灶！（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕烧不干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派些老总照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅屋一小伢，（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧做虾蟆叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大人被捉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没有人捞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化骨又扬灰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变做两头鬼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙倒壁又塌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老总们好笑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三处点着火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看奥不奥？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民政府放的官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个顾命的敢告？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉了老百姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带上七里坪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开了法堂审："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“‘奸匪’活不成！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗地又传信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“送钱不要紧。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要托人去说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先拿钱来塞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵卖婆娘伢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢说“没得”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情下了地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把钱没得罪。（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多的十万几，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回去赶粜下锅米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜穷光蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该你拿命抵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怨只怨爹娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不该贫如洗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）抢光、杀光、烧光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）上官，地名，是解放区；么样即怎样；队子就是队伍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）倒霉的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）小伢即小孩子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）把钱即给钱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}